isUnique

public boolean isUnique()
                 throws com.essbase.api.base.EssException
Returns if the Uniqueness at Generation is enabled or disabled.

Returns:
if true, the members at this generation cannot have duplicate member names; otherwise false to indicate duplicate member names at this gen are allowed.
Throws:
com.essbase.api.base.EssException - if an error occurs.
